Separuh orang luar,

259
00:14:41,559 --> 00:14:42,720
dan separuh orang baru.

260
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:45,679
Mungkin organisasi patut fikir semula.

261
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:47,360
Bolehkah aku

262
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,960
benar-benar lakukan ini?

263
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,720
Dari sudut positif,

264
00:14:53,279 --> 00:14:55,000
masa depan kau masih cerah.

265
00:14:56,759 --> 00:14:58,840
Sebab kau orang baru dan orang luar,

266
00:14:59,759 --> 00:15:01,360
keliru itu perkara biasa.

267
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,879
Tapi jangan terlalu melampau.

268
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,399
Tianshuang,

269
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:09,919
tak kira apa orang lain fikir,

270
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:14,639
atau apa yang kau fikir,

271
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,879
ini kebenaran yang tak boleh dinafikan.

272
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,440
Perjuangan kita perlukan kau.

273
00:15:20,559 --> 00:15:21,440
Aku perlukan kau.

274
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,679
Setiap kawan di sisi kau mengharapkan kau.

275
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:30,960
Kau pasti?

276
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,360
Sebab aku tahu

277
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,240
dengan kau di situ,

278
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:38,799
sama ada di Lian'an Town

279
00:15:39,639 --> 00:15:41,159
atau di mana-mana saja,

280
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:43,320
segalanya akan baik-baik saja

281
00:15:43,919 --> 00:15:45,440
pada akhirnya.

282
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:52,159
Kita dah dewasa.

283
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:53,159
Masih nak bagi kata-kata semangat?

284
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,960
Baiklah, jangan pujuk aku lagi.

285
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,240
Aku takkan berputus asa.

286
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,120
Aku ikhlas.

287
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,320
Baiklah, kata-kata ikhlas.

288
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,519
Masa kau datang,

289
00:16:05,639 --> 00:16:06,799
kau tak nak buat.

290
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,120
Tapi lepas baca diari Tianliang,

291
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,039
kau ubah fikiran.

292
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,519
Tianliang sangat penakut,

293
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,159
tapi tetap berpegang pada pendiriannya.

294
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,360
Jadi aku fikir,

295
00:16:24,919 --> 00:16:26,440
sebab aku yang masih hidup,

296
00:16:27,759 --> 00:16:29,320
aku tak boleh berdiam diri saja.

297
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,759
Kalau tidak, dia pasti marah.

298
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,240
Betul tak?

299
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,759
Anggap saja ini sebagai penebusan.

300
00:16:38,279 --> 00:16:39,679
Ini bukan penebusan.

301
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,200
Ini permulaan baru.

302
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,240
Tianshuang,

303
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,720
dengar sini.

304
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,279
Apa yang berlaku dulu,

305
00:16:50,799 --> 00:16:52,039
bukan salah kau.

306
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:53,960
Aku tahu.

307
00:16:57,039 --> 00:16:58,240
Aku ulang sekali lagi.

308
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,440
Bukan salah kau.

309
00:17:03,039 --> 00:17:03,679
Aku tahu.

310
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,960
Kau tak tahu!

311
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,559
Memang bukan salah kau!

312
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,440
Betul ke?

313
00:17:42,749 --> 00:17:46,611
♪Bila nama terkubur dalam debu♪

314
00:17:46,813 --> 00:17:50,111
♪Masih ada degupan jantung
menembusi fajar dan senja♪

315
00:17:50,141 --> 00:17:53,893
♪Jika tiada tepukan di penghujungnya♪

316
00:17:54,301 --> 00:18:00,278
♪Sekurang-kurangnya bayang-bayang
masih membentuk insan♪

